properties.name: plot
properties.sample: A mother and daughter con team seduce and scam wealthy men.

properties.name: fullplot
properties.sample: Max and Page are a mother and daughter con team. Max seduces wealthy men into marrying her, then Page seduces them into infidelity so Max can rake them over the divorce court coals. And then it's on to the next victim.

properties.name: consensus
properties.sample: Though the actors pour a lot of energy into their roles, Heartbreakers is too drawn out, and the romantic subplot doesn't blend well. Also, the con women aren't particularly sympathetic.
